OL,3,CRussell Brand's rape trial delayed
OL,4,Cuntil October
OL,6,FRussell Brand's trial over allegations
OL,7,Fof rape and sexual assault has been
OL,8,Fdelayed until October.
OL,10,FThe comedian and actor, 50, is accused
OL,11,Fof three counts of rape, three charges
OL,12,Fof sexual assault, and one allegation
OL,13,Fof indecent assault, with six women
OL,14,Falleging crimes dating from 1999 to
OL,15,F2009. He denies them all.
OL,17,FBrand was first charged in April 2025
OL,18,Fwith alleged offences against four of
OL,19,Fthe women, and his trial was set to
OL,20,Fstart on June 16 this year at
OL,21,FSouthwark Crown Court.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/5
