OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1774980702
OL,3,CRussell Brand's rape trial delayed
OL,4,Cuntil October
OL,6,FFresh charges involving two new
OL,7,Fcomplainants were brought in January
OL,8,Fand, at a hearing on Monday, Mr
OL,9,FJustice Bennathan agreed to delay the
OL,10,Ftrial until October 12.
OL,12,FBrand was not present in court for
OL,13,FMonday's hearing, but was represented
OL,14,Fby barrister Ian Winter KC.
OL,16,FThe comedian has previously appeared
OL,17,Ftwice at the courthouse to enter not
OL,18,Fguilty pleas to all the allegations he
OL,19,Ffaces.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/5
