PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1774980702
OL,3,CRussell Brand's rape trial delayed
OL,4,Cuntil October
OL,6,FThe court heard the original trial was
OL,7,Fscheduled for up to five weeks, but is
OL,8,Fnow expected to last for around two
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FThe judge said if Brand's trial
OL,12,Fstarted in mid-June, the court may run
OL,13,Fout of time to hear it and would
OL,14,Fstruggle to find jurors who could sit
OL,15,Fthrough the start of the summer
OL,16,Fholidays.
OL,18,FAt the hearing on Monday, the judge
OL,19,Fformally joined together the two sets
OL,20,Fof charges that Brand faces.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/5
