OL,3,CRussell Brand's rape trial delayed
OL,4,Cuntil October
OL,6,FDuring a showbiz career which started
OL,7,Fin the 90s, Brand was one of Britain's
OL,8,Fbest-known stand-up comedians and
OL,9,Fpresented Big Brother spin-off shows
OL,10,FBig Brother's Big Mouth and Big
OL,11,FBrother: Celebrity Hijack.
OL,13,FBrand starred in a host of Hollywood
OL,14,Ffilms and in recent years and he has
OL,15,Frecently moved into podcasting and
OL,16,Fonline influencing.
OL,18,FBrand, who has a home in
OL,19,FBuckinghamshire but now lives in the
OL,20,FUnited States, has been granted bail
OL,21,Fduring the criminal proceedings.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/5
