OL,6,FBrand, who has a home in
OL,7,FBuckinghamshire but now lives in the
OL,8,FUnited States, has been granted bail
OL,9,Fduring the criminal proceedings.
OL,11,FA further two-day pre-trial hearing in
OL,12,Fhis case has been set for June 16 and
OL,13,F17.
